divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside at 11:12 last night when I looked to the north and I saw a strange light in the sky then I saw what looked like a shooting star come past it or from it it just emitted for a second. I was looking at the stars because I thought I seen a cluster of stars and the Milky Way in the sky at the time. A plane but it made no sound It was flying from east to west over the highway and the road that I live on I had thought I saw at first a shooting star and I thought it had hit the object then I thought it had come off the object It just flew to the west over a road and highway
